text: Amid record-breaking heat, the California Independent System Operator, which oversees the state’s electric power system, warned that people could see power shut offs on Sunday if the entire state did not do their part to conserve energy. https://t.co/oZkmkglZTs

text: With three weeks left in the 2020 season, San Francisco Giants manager Gabe Kapler is “managing baseball games with some sense of urgency” as his team makes a push for the National League playoffs. https://t.co/dckbkTYSse
